        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Future Century Gaming Pty Ltd operates an online gaming platform targeting players aged 18−40 in Australia. It has been in operation since 2012, providing subscription access to a variety of online games.\n\nThe business is considering expanding into emerging global markets but is finding it challenging to recruit and retain skilled, qualified game designers and developers in Australia. It is considering international labour markets to overcome staff shortages.\n\nThe business has decided to finance its expansion into global markets through\nexternal sources."
        }
